name: Sparrow Design system（preview）
description:
This is my recent design. I'll preview it for you. I hope you can leave me a message about the problems you find.

It is a set of specification library. Let's talk about the problems we know first. Because of the time relationship, the components are not standardized and the naming is not standardized. These will be changed later.

这是我最近做的设计，给各位预览下，希望给我留言你发现的问题。

是一套规范库，先说下自己知道的问题，因为时间关系，组件不规范、命名也不规范。这些后面会改的。
